com.facebook.buck.rules.coercer

Class SourceSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.coercer.SourceSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddsToRuleKey, TargetTranslatable<SourceSet>

    public abstract class SourceSet
extends Object
implements TargetTranslatable<SourceSet>, AddsToRuleKey
    A group of ordered sources, stored as either a Set of unnamed SourcePaths or a Map of names to SourcePaths. Commonly used to represent the input srcs parameter of rules where source "names" may be important (e.g. to control layout of C++ headers).
